**who —** The Evil One — the skeletal, alien final boss — emerged from a fallen meteorite, it twisted the Dwarves into monsters and turned them on the Elves; only the Dragon Slayer sword can end it (no other name survives in the record)

**what —** the skeletal, alien final boss — emerged from a fallen meteorite, it twisted the Dwarves into monsters and turned them on the Elves; only the Dragon Slayer sword can end it (no other name survives in the record)

