**why —** It is the corruption at the crown of the world: a horror that fell from the sky, poisoned a tree, and made monsters of a people who were not its enemy.

**how —** Crystallized from Faxanadu (NES 1989) — Famicom Xanadu, on Falcom's licensed Xanadu name.

**◌ the mythos —** It is the corruption at the crown of the world: a horror that fell from the sky, poisoned a tree, and made monsters of a people who were not its enemy. a being of the World Tree and the climb to the Evil One

